title: Circus Debate
itunes:title: Circus Debate
description:
Today on the show after an embarrassing display for the American people, we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about the first Presidential debate, which many where displeased by both parties performance. Moreover, Charlamagne ended up giving our celebrity and chief Donald Trump "Donkey of the Day" and Angela Yee helped some listeners with "Ask Yee"
